FBIS4-23457 "drafr109_b_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-109 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 EAST AFRICA Uganda Museveni Calls For War Crimes Trial for Rwanda Museveni Calls For War Crimes Trial for Rwanda PM0706083694 Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 4 Jun 94 p 14 PM0706083694 Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE Danish BFN [Text] Copenhagen -- During a working visit to Denmark Ugandan President Yoweri Kaguta Museveni said yesterday that a war crimes trial like the Nuremberg trials should be started under the auspices of the United Nations to find those responsible for the massacres in Rwanda. He also criticized the United Nations for the "superficial" way in which the world organization has tackled the civil war in Rwanda.
